    "patch_code": "public int elementSiblingIndex() {\n    Validate.notNull(this);\n\n    ArrayList childrens = new ArrayList<>((Collection<E>) parent().children());\n    for (int i = 0; i < childrens.size(); i++) {\n         E child = childrens.get(i);\n         if (child.equals(this)){\n             return i;\n         }\n    }\n    return -1;\n}",
